itl.enabler.api

Interface AttendantCollection.AttendantCollectionEventListener

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.util.EventListener
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AttendantCollection.AttendantCollectionEventAdapter
    Enclosing class:
    AttendantCollection

    public static interface AttendantCollection.AttendantCollectionEventListener
extends java.util.EventListener
    Listens to events from every Attendant in the collection.
    Clients can either implement this interface to receive events on the whole Attendant Collection or subscribe to events from individual attendantsByNum.
    See Also:
    Attendant.AttendantEventListener
